ces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></blockquote><br />\n唔可以咁！寧願落老蘭扮現充都好過毒自在家<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f029bbae695ceb47d336d1937718d1678e65f7","tid":15163,"uid":2792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:01:45.000Z","msg":"除夕咁都人就唔想出街"},{"pid":"4aea26327073b13e983f4be49263426f8134d0b7","tid":15163,"uid":2792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除夕咁多人就唔想出街</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ea9acba7b3b48699aa91d5dc4d392cf89605c5b4","tid":15163,"uid":45923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:26:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>除夕咁多人就唔想出街</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n你咁講令我諗起幾年前尖沙咀倒數完，走果時俾人偷銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自此以後我都冇再去倒數"},{"pid":"17670e0facb83a9edc7c1d2f5c967b27201aaf7f","tid":15163,"uid":2792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除夕咁多人就唔想出街</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n你咁講令我諗起幾年前尖沙咀倒數完，走果時俾人偷銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自此以後我都冇再去倒數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁慘!!肯定係偷?定係跌左咋<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 有年諗住去尖沙咀同d fd食埋飯倒數,<br />\n係旺角一落地鐵站就呼吸唔到,<br />\n即刻飛機左d fd番左屋企附近食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a007ea17483c2797111ee1dd449e0ad6526eb2","tid":15163,"uid":45923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:00:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除夕咁多人就唔想出街</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n你咁講令我諗起幾年前尖沙咀倒數完，走果時俾人偷銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自此以後我都冇再去倒數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁慘!!肯定係偷?定係跌左咋<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 有年諗住去尖沙咀同d fd食埋飯倒數,<br />\n係旺角一落地鐵站就呼吸唔到,<br />\n即刻飛機左d fd番左屋企附近食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯撚定！走果時人迫迫完全冇空間可言，我估扒手就係喱d時間zip隻手來偷我野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上除夕如果怕人多，老蘭、時代廣場、尖沙咀海傍係唔去得。但除左喱3個地方之外都冇咩地方有倒數氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}